Architecture: all
Depends: redis-server, php-cli, systemd,
 alternc (>> 3.2.10),
 ${misc:Depends}
Description: Redis module for AlternC
 AlternC is a mutualized hosting software manager for Linux.
 It allows you to manage your websites, domains, ftp, emails, aliases,
 web statistics, mailing-lists, etc.
 .
 This package is an optional module that adds redis-server management
 to the virtual desktop. Any user having a redis quota above 0 can then
 ask for the laucnh of its own secured redis-server using Unix Socket.
 .
 More information on https://www.alternc.com/
